    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"quill\"\ndescription: \"A text editor for R\"\nauthor:\n  - name: Álvaro Sánchez\n    url: https://svalvaro.github.io/\ndate: 19-11-2024\ncategories: [R, quill, shiny]\nimage: quill.png\ndraft: false \nfreeze: true\n---\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\nlibrary(quill)\nquill(toolbar_options(image = FALSE, video = FALSE))\n```\n\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"quillWidget html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-c8d81381f31490ff79c5\" style=\"width:100%;height:464px;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-c8d81381f31490ff79c5\">{\"x\":{\"toolbar_options\":{\"align\":[{\"align\":\"center\"},{\"align\":\"right\"}],\"background\":[{\"background\":[]}],\"color\":[{\"color\":[]}],\"direction\":[{\"direction\":\"rtl\"}],\"header\":[{\"header\":[\"1\",\"2\",false,\"3\"]}],\"indent\":[{\"indent\":\"-1\"},{\"indent\":\"+1\"}],\"list\":[{\"list\":\"ordered\"},{\"list\":\"bullet\"},{\"list\":\"check\"}],\"size\":[{\"size\":[\"small\",true,\"large\",\"huge\"]}],\"script\":[{\"script\":\"sub\"},{\"script\":\"super\"}],\"binary_options\":[\"blockquote\",\"bold\",\"clean\",\"formula\",\"code\",\"italic\",\"link\",\"strike\",\"underline\",\"code-block\"]},\"theme\":\"snow\",\"placeholder\":\"Placeholder message\"},\"evals\":[],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\nThe Quill package makes it easy to:\n\n- Add a modern text editor to Shiny apps or R Markdown documents.\n- Customize the toolbar to include options like bold, italics, headers, or links.\n- Retrieve and process user input in real-time.\nLessons Learned\n\n\nCode in [GitHub](https://github.com/svalvaro/quill){target=\"_blank\"}",
